text.div: • Include codes from http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v3-EntityCode where concept is-a KIT

name: KitEntityType
title: KitEntityType
description: A container for a diverse collection of products intended to be used together for some purpose (e.g. Medicinal kits often contain a syringe, a needle and the injectable medication).
